{"tid":1862890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撚屌戴口罩亂扔垃圾以為戴左口罩就無人認得佢","createTime":"2020-02-05T01:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T05:34:00.000Z","uid":214261,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49d2793f59b1c9769f61a26ffe560c613200df3c","tid":1862890,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Umd4QU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Umd4QU.png&h=3939ba34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxTgia2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxTgia2.png&h=21c5d3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔幫手認下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係見到佢對眼已經睇得出一副窮酸相同係廢中樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n瘋狂屌柒佢扮聽唔到<br />\n巴士食野都算<br />\n而家已經武漢肺炎周街都係菌<br />\n仲要食完啲包裝紙攝係凳邊<br />\n<br />\n之後再忍唔住屌佢<br />\n佢叫我收聲 唔好嘈<br />\n之後好彩有個小妹妹幫口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多謝你呀<br />\n香港咁嘅時勢已經好少咁熱心嘅人<br />\n<br />\n最後係度呼籲，保持環境清潔，人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698a022302f194fbd668052cb275cd36f5ff0f51","tid":1862890,"uid":214261,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:12:11.000Z","msg":"窮撚廿鳩幾歲仲要依賴交通工具是否悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4f2b460609fc690c2ecca42039344407d0b7d3","tid":1862890,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b3014851d422f4823ec0073ee4364c4d4e8174f8","tid":1862890,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:16:09.000Z","msg":"應該當年係件好型棍既mk囝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b9f96f329ec76c242037481f41f14a5756a0eb","tid":1862890,"uid":11447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02